captions.text: "Improbable Scenes", ladies and gentlemen!

You wrote some scene
suggestions for us out there,

put them in the red box, I'll
read the suggestions for them

and I'll see what they
do when they hear...
'Ways to go through a flood'.
Dammit.

- Flood, right?
- Let's do it?
Sure!

- The car...
- I ended up on this side...
It's not functional, but it's beautiful!
Oh, no...

- Flood?
- Yeah...
Wait.

- Don't be stupid, man!
- What?

- It's better to use a glass...
- Thanks, I didn't have a glass with me...
I'm glad I'm riding a bee...
Guys! Guys! Paulistas!

- It's water!
- Water!

- I have a water tank in my trunk!
- Hurry! Go get it!

Okay! 'Improbable ways to annoy
the guy next to you in the theatre'.

'Improbable ways to annoy the
guy next to you in the theatre'.

- Can you just...
- I love this song!

This is just tre instrumental version...
When she sings...
Hey, buddy!

Could you sing louder?
This is beautiful!

- Excuse me...
- What?
I think this is my chair!

- The movie is almost over! - Yeah,
but I can't see it very well from here...

Sorry! Excuse me!
Sorry! Excuse me!

Sorry! Sorry!
Excuse me! Thanks! Sorry!
Excuse me! Excuse me!

Sorry! Sorry!
Sorry! Excuse me!
Rogério, it's here!

You'll see the 'worst pick-up
lines from a poll worker'!
Your ID number...

Wow! Your ID number is a
lot like my phone number!

Can I give my justification
for liking you?
I guess my section is another one!
How are you?
Well, I have to say this...

Of all the 38 Adrianas that
went here, you're the finest!

Now, some 'unseen scenes from
the Castelo Rá-Tim-Bum kids show'.

How cute! 'Unseen scenes
from Castelo Rá-Tim-Bum'!
Nino! Let's play!
Have you never noticed my size?

I'm not in the age for
playing with you brats!
I told you Nino was on drugs, guys!
Nino!
Let's end this, I have OCD!

I have this hair gel,
put this fuckin' hair down!
This is getting on my nerves!
Little bird! What is this sound?
Oh shit, the cops!
Little bird! What is this sound?

We're the sparrows, man!
Here's the deal...
Little bird! What is this sound?

This is the sound of
uncle Victor having sex!
Improbable scenes, ladies and gentlemen!
